OL,3,CCovid Inquiry: Care worker describes
OL,4,C'hardest day' losing three residents
OL,6,FITV Wales health reporter Katie Fenton
OL,7,Fspoke to care home manager Navjit Kaur
OL,8,Fabout her reflections on the pandemic.
OL,10,FA care home manager in the Vale of
OL,11,FGlamorgan has described the day she
OL,12,Flost three residents to Covid-19 as
OL,13,Fthe "hardest day" of her career.
OL,15,FSpringbank Care Home manager Navjit
OL,16,FKaur, who was then working as the
OL,17,Fhome's Clinical Lead, said staff were
OL,18,Fgiven "no support" and "no guidance"
OL,19,Fat the start of the pandemic.
