OL,3,CCovid Inquiry: Care worker describes
OL,4,C'hardest day' losing three residents
OL,6,FIt comes as the Covid-19 Inquiry has
OL,7,Fbeen hearing from experts in the care
OL,8,Fsector and bereaved families from
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FProfessor Stephen Barclay, an expert
OL,12,Fin end-of-life and palliative care,
OL,13,Ftold the Inquiry that care home
OL,14,Fmanagers "struggled with the almost
OL,15,Fdaily changes in guidance and advice
OL,16,Fand regulations".
OL,18,FThe Inquiry is coming to the end of
OL,19,Fits current module, which has focussed
OL,20,Fon the pandemic's impact on the adult
OL,21,Fcare sector.
