OL,3,CCovid Inquiry: Care worker describes
OL,4,C'hardest day' losing three residents
OL,6,FReflecting on the start of the
OL,7,Fpandemic, Ms Kaur said it was a
OL,8,F"scary" and "traumatic" experience for
OL,9,Fcolleagues and residents alike.
OL,11,FShe said: "We didn't know what to do.
OL,12,FThere was no guidance, there was no
OL,13,Fadvice. We didn't have enough PPE. We
OL,14,Fhad only gloves and aprons, but we
OL,15,Fdidn't have provision of masks.
OL,17,F"Every day was a challenge," Ms Kaur
OL,18,Fadded.
