OL,6,FShe added: "The emotional impact that
OL,7,Fwe all have had, I don't think I can
OL,8,Fget over all my life."
OL,10,FMs Kaur said that guidance did improve
OL,11,Fafter a couple of months when local
OL,12,Fgovernment and Public Health Wales
OL,13,Fstarted getting more involved and
OL,14,Fissuing further advice to care homes.
OL,16,FWednesday's (30 July) Inquiry
OL,17,Fdiscussions come after the former
OL,18,FFirst Minister of Wales, Mark
OL,19,FDrakeford, previously admitted Wales
OL,20,Fwas "not as prepared as it could have
OL,21,Fbeen" for a pandemic.
